{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that young man gave his life for that-- he could have survived because he was Polish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could speak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because all the Polish Jews was-- had a better chance of survival than-- than-- And then one day, they brought over a machine to dig-- to dig trenches because they didn't have enough room for the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to-- to take the soil away from the digging machine on a heap with all the [INAUDIBLE] we could dig up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a Dutch boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- we used to call him Caruso.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that Frenzel didn't like him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they told us, you know, the musicians had sometimes to play, and who can sing had to sing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to-- you know, they used to come and listen or just amuse themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't like the Dutch boy, that Caruso.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So each time that boy used to come-- he was maybe about 17.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to come around with that [INAUDIBLE] of soil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He hit him, and he was beaten that hard that he didn't survive the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning, he was-- he was gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was so sad, so cruel, because everybody loved him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was such good looking, and he still wasn't so thin like others because he wasn't there very long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to a lot of us, you know, happened, if he didn't like somebody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wagner ?] had night duties, he needed every morning when he used to come after the-- it was finished-- 5 o'clock or 6 o'clock in the morning-- with his big Shepherd dog.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He used to pull out for no reason somebody from the sleeping quarters and execute.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not-- not always in front.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
